make_grid[source]

make_grid(path, gridsize_x:int=640, gridsize_y:int=480, overlap:Tuple[int, int]=(100, 100))

Creates a grid template with gridsize_x times gridsize_y cells, with overlap pixels of overlap based on geotiff file in path. Returns a gpd.GeoDataFrame with RyyCxx identifier for each geometry
